{"tid":2175482,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Wifi extender一問","createTime":"2020-08-26T13:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T07:15:36.000Z","uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98946adec098782d33b694ad943cbe0f3de5b950","tid":2175482,"uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我弟屋企嘅網速如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxeP6d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxeP6d7.jpg&h=a8cbe138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但一入到房就得返咁嘅速度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7UXvF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7UXvF7.jpg&h=d780414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗慢咗仲成日斷線<br />\n嚟緊就嚟開學要網上授課<br />\n想喺間房都有穩定網速<br />\n屋企四百呎左右<br />\nRouter喺屋企最左邊但間房喺最右邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪應該買Wifi extender<br />\n如果係應該買咩型號<br />\n速度唔洗好快但希望可以穩定唔會斷線<br />\n求各位師兄教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32ac7406840832bd592a8edc0825e6efc304fdc","tid":2175482,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f2500cdd8634e1a625f4113a4d3c4ddd79e0fd7","tid":2175482,"uid":367354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f32ac7406840832bd592a8edc0825e6efc304fdc","tid":2175482,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望有Ching解答下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aca15c08c4544754d2505e2a35ce6dac23560dd","tid":2175482,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"平面圖<br />\n咩上網<br />\n咩ROUTER"},{"pid":"b437a8ea0d2c0ca8dfc93c7b22c74b7d9f5cb7e5","tid":2175482,"uid":367354,"like":0,"disl